	Patch from Tom Parker <palfrey@tevp.net>:

	* src/Makefile.am (CPPFLAGS): Switch to AM_CPPFLAGS.
	
	* src/backends/NetworkManagerRedHat.c: Switch to
	including shvar.h instead of shvar.c.

